---
title: Mild Caribbean Spiced Fish with Pineapple Salsa & Garlic-Spinach Rice
description: Caribbean spice is such a party for your mouth that we had to step up every element of this lively dish, from the pineapple and salsa to the garlic-spinach rice. Packed with flavour and ready in a flash – what's not to love?
